                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18431023-name-1176" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-1176" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-1176" type="surname" value="BROWN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-1176" type="given" value="WILLIAM HENRY"></interp>WILLIAM HENRY BROWN</persName>
                  </hi>. I keep a beer-shop in Bowling-green-lane, Clerkenwell. On the evening of the 24th of Oct., the prisoner came for half a pint of ale—he went into the bar parlour—I saw him take this quart pot, and put it into his pocket—when he went out, I went and stopped him—I told him he had a pot—he said he had no such thing about him—I gave him into custody—the pot was found between my house and where I stopped him.</p>
